 150:indcpa.c      **** * Arguments:   - polyvec *a: pointer to ouptput matrix A
 151:indcpa.c      **** *              - const uint8_t *seed: pointer to input seed
 152:indcpa.c      **** *              - int transposed: boolean deciding whether A or A^T is generated
